rows.label: tlk41700122_02_msg0001
rows.name:
That water tower's well good
and busted now.

rows.label: tlk41700122_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Thankfully, we can get by for
the moment drawing water
from Coolley Lake...

rows.label: tlk41700122_02_msg0003
rows.name:
But some of the lakes around here
are contaminated, so I'm a little worried
about how it'll affect our crops.

rows.label: tlk41700122_02_msg0004
rows.name:
What use is it having the Empire's
strongest Driver around if she can't
even do anything when villains attack?

rows.label: tlk41700122_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I sure hope the Superbian army catch
whoever was responsible for this mess.
